author: Annie Brown
title: The Tiny Trump is making the internet great again
text:
The Tiny Trump is making the internet great again Annie Brown twitter TWEET More 
In a week that has given us the former Swedish foreign minister Carl Bildt asking in a tweet what President Donald Trump had "been smoking," in response to Trump's mysterious statements about Sweden , it seems fitting that a remarkable new internet meme has arrived: Tiny Donald Trump. 
No, it's not to do with Trump's hands, which are normal size, even "slightly large, actually." SHARE Tiny Trump is the latest meme to capture the internet's fancy. Photo: Twitter 
Well, it could be, but who wants to look a gift horse in the mouth? The joke originated on a Reddit community called Tiny Trumps late last week and has since flooded the internet, with pranksters having a whole lot of fun inserting the itsy-bitsy sized president into various scenarios (historical, diplomatic and imagined).
